{"image_id": "WU_2018_page_186", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "2018 FORM 10-K", "bbox": [6.2, 1271.4, 50.8, 1560.3]}, {"text": "90", "bbox": [609.0, 1554.9, 629.0, 1583.0]}, {"text": "THE WESTERN UNION COMPANY", "bbox": [447.9, 110.9, 795.0, 138.7]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS (Continued)", "bbox": [287.0, 159.8, 956.4, 187.6]}, {"text": "mitigated, as in most cases the Company requires the receipt of funds from customers before releasing the associated cross-", "bbox": [113.3, 208.0, 1124.8, 235.5]}, {"text": "currency payment.", "bbox": [113.3, 232.1, 273.5, 259.5]}, {"text": "Settlement obligations consist of money transfer, money order and payment service payables and payables to agents.", "bbox": [150.8, 281.1, 1130.1, 308.5]}, {"text": "Money transfer payables represent amounts to be paid to transferees when they request their funds. Most agents typically", "bbox": [113.3, 305.0, 1130.9, 332.4]}, {"text": "settle with transferees first and then obtain reimbursement from the Company. Money order payables represent amounts", "bbox": [113.3, 329.0, 1129.8, 356.4]}, {"text": "not yet presented for payment. Payment service payables represent amounts to be paid to utility companies, auto finance", "bbox": [113.3, 353.0, 1130.0, 380.4]}, {"text": "companies, mortgage servicers, financial service providers, government agencies and others. Due to the agent funding and", "bbox": [113.3, 376.9, 1129.8, 404.3]}, {"text": "settlement process, payables to agents represent amounts due to agents for money transfers that have been settled with", "bbox": [113.3, 400.9, 1130.1, 428.3]}, {"text": "transferees.", "bbox": [113.3, 424.9, 213.8, 452.3]}, {"text": "Settlement assets and obligations consisted of the following (in millions):", "bbox": [150.8, 473.8, 769.2, 501.2]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [972.7, 525.1, 1078.1, 547.3]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [951.0, 545.4, 988.6, 567.5]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [1062.4, 545.4, 1099